      %h2 About Rugged Tree Woodworking
      %p We founded this business because we love the peices that have been passed down to us, and wanted to enable others to pass down quality woodwork for generations to come. Each piece has a story; when it entered the family, the people that used it, the names carved in the back. Those stories keep us connected to our heritage, and give us something to remember the ones that are no longer with us.
